# ============================================================
# Unity 工程 Git 忽略规则
# 原则：只上传 Assets 目录内容（含 .meta）+ 项目配置文件
# ============================================================

# ---- Unity 自动生成的本地缓存和临时文件 ----
[Ll]ibrary/
[Tt]emp/
[Oo]bj/
[Bb]uild/
[Bb]uilds/
[Ll]ogs/
[Mm]emoryCaptures/
[Rr]ecordings/

# ---- VS / IDE ----
.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.csproj
*.unityproj

# ---- 操作系统垃圾文件 ----
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ---- 不应该上传的大文件/编译产物 ----
*.apk
*.aab
*.unitypackage
*.app
*.exe
*.dll
*.pdb
*.mdb
